	measure 'Held Securities Changes Title DQ' = ```
			
			VAR FW =
			    SELECTEDVALUE ( Framework[Framework Display] )
			VAR _min =
			    EDATE ( MIN ( 'Period'[End of Month] ), -1 )
			VAR MIN_PRD =
			    VALUE ( YEAR ( _min ) & FORMAT ( MONTH ( _min ), "00" ) )
			VAR MAX_PRD = MAX('Period'[Period])
			VAR startDate =
			    CALCULATE (
			        MAX('Securities'[As Of Dt]),
			        'Securities'[As of Period] = MIN_PRD
			    )
			VAR endDate =
			    CALCULATE (
			        MAX ( 'Securities'[As Of Dt] ),
			        'Securities'[As of Period] = MAX_PRD
			    )
			RETURN
			    "Held Securities Changes, " & FW & ", "
			        & FORMAT ( startDate, "dd-mmm-yy" ) & " - "
			        & FORMAT ( endDate, "dd-mmm-yy" )
			
			```
		displayFolder: Security Changes Measures
		lineageTag: 6824d37e-8c6c-4adc-ab0a-d5a11f684583

